{"tid":1532750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家係香港地，popo仲大過共產黨","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T18:13:26.000Z","uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d66aa4a3bdbb04a63bcdb83eee37f624114689d9","tid":1532750,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/04151802/sdgasgwegwegwe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F04151802%2Fsdgasgwegwegwe.png&h=c81cd3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄧小平在1987年會見基本法起草委員會時曾經表示，「有些事情，比如1997年後香港有人罵罵中國共產黨、罵中國，我們還是允許他罵...」<br />\n<br />\n鄧小平曾說:「我們不怕他們罵，共產黨是罵不倒的」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/236878/王志民要港人尊重共產黨%E3%80%80鄧小平曾稱「還是允許/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F236878%2F%E7%8E%8B%E5%BF%97%E6%B0%91%E8%A6%81%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8%25E3%2580%2580%E9%84%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%B3%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E5%85%81%E8%A8%B1%2F&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1ap1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=a1bba4b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/236878/王志民要港人尊重共產黨%E3%80%80鄧小平曾稱「還是允許/</a><br />\n<br />\n而家市民批判popo兩句都俾防暴又拉又鎖又爆頭，我地納稅人養班popo原來唔鬧得架<br />\n<br />\n所以話popo大過共產黨，直逼當年日本皇軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2afa6b361290829d839f3625646dd7eccae5de","tid":1532750,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"下次唔好鬧黑警，直接叫返一個恰如其分嘅稱呼:<span style=\"color: red;\">法西斯</span>"},{"pid":"8b0ac2726a365d74a09c14776b6320da763d16a5","tid":1532750,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44f88ad5e2a22a0ef7b3aa72e6f142f4f1118bca","tid":1532750,"uid":132497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:16:5